Subject: OOO - Delay in Responding RE: PLEASE HOLD - revising Conoco quote
BodyText:
This email originated outside of TD SYNNEX.  Please help keep our organization and partners safe. It's up to us; think before you click.


Hello,

I’ll be out of the office on PTO this week and will have limited
access to my email. I value your message and will do my best to
respond as soon as possible. However, please be prepared for delays in
my responses. For urgent matters, please call my mobile at
832-512-9728, and I’ll get back to you as soon as I can.

I appreciate your patience and understanding. Thank you.

Best regards,

Alan

--

The content of this email message and any attachments are intended solely
